{"tid":1057340,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"四年oral5**《半個鐘講解小組討論2012-2018頭兩日題目要點》","createTime":"2019-03-11T22:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T16:53:04.000Z","uid":80833,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ee10a03ff37b327f8d890e3f3eb54b0af14f9a","tid":1057340,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:17:04.000Z","msg":"大家好，我曾經都係呢到做過相似既教學。<br />\n都唔算太熱切，可能自己教學唔算太好啦。<br />\n不過唔緊要，今日會係考oral第一日，好多考生都懵懵下。<br />\n因此，就整左呢段片出來，希望可以幫到大家去考好oral。<br />\n內容係2012-2018頭兩日題目要點。<br />\n<br />\n小弟四年5**，基本上2012-2018頭所有oral題目，都自行演練思考過一次。<br />\n所以，真係係學校練六個鐘，不如聽我講半個鐘。<br />\n主要希望可以構建一個免費既平台出來等大家都可以戰勝dse，尤其係第一份卷oral<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢話唔多講，片就係到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWbHoFb4tVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWbHoFb4tVU&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6DH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=ab6148da\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWbHoFb4tVU</a><br />\n<br />\n經過整合，呢兩日題目最會可能出既範圍係<br />\n1.青少年特質<br />\n2.人生意義<br />\n3.社會環境<br />\n4.待人之道<br />\n5.五倫之德<br />\n<br />\n這五種topic係片都有講到<br />\n大家加油<br />\n都希望我既學生可以同大家互相配合，旗開得勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c985ec1cd3499455cfb56babab66355055028f1","tid":1057340,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:19:27.000Z","msg":"有乜驅使你考咁多年？"},{"pid":"76d3dd84a620658fa109447619e3816f835c400d","tid":1057340,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c985ec1cd3499455cfb56babab66355055028f1","tid":1057340,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:19:27.000Z","msg":"有乜驅使你考咁多年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T22:20:55.000Z","msg":"熱愛"},{"pid":"1c91fe6a2fd09397ae6c3ea22ae9a6dabf790411","tid":1057340,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc